          <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "PRL is a tag that has function of marking a list of parenthetic"@en .


###  http://purl.org/ncor-br/c-oral/SCA
coral:SCA rdf:type owl:Class ;
          rdfs:subClassOf coral:tag ,
