          <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "SCA"@en ;
          <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "SCA is a tag that has function of marking a scanning"@en .


###  http://purl.org/ncor-br/c-oral/TMT
coral:TMT rdf:type owl:Class ;
          rdfs:subClassOf coral:tag ,
